    • Enum Constant Detail

      • FP_MODE_VIDEO

        public static final FacialProcessing.FP_MODES FP_MODE_VIDEO
        Use this to configure the facial processing framework to the video mode. This will set the facial processing scan to only perform complete image scans on every fifteenth frame while tracking detected faces in between in order to reduce the overhead of scanning for faces where the image input is a set of image frames, like that coming from the camera preview.

      • FP_MODE_STILL

        public static final FacialProcessing.FP_MODES FP_MODE_STILL
        Use this to configure the facial processing framework to still mode. This will set the facial processing framework to completely scan each image for faces. This is best when passing in static images for processing.
